Education: BS – Metropolitan State College of Denver
Member of CFA Institute and CFA Society Colorado

Derek Anguilm, CFA is a co-director of Value research, a portfolio manager and analyst on the Value team at Denver Investments. He is also a partner at the firm. Prior to joining the Value team in 2002, Mr. Anguilm worked as a wealth management analyst at the firm. He began his career as a research assistant with Everen Securities. Mr. Anguilm received a BS from Metropolitan State College of Denver. He is a CFA® charterholder and a member of CFA Institute and CFA Society Colorado.
